{"tid":2188891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國示威29 人被捕　人權律師獄中信籲 9.19 再集會 / 傳 泰國政府取消同中國既280億美元隧道項目！","createTime":"2020-09-04T13:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T14:15:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de71e78ba1ca821d6b12284f2aa3ad18d6bf68a2","tid":2188891,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/泰國示威至今共29人被捕-被控煽動人權律師不獲保釋-獄中寫信呼籲9-19再集會/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%85%B129%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%AB%E4%BF%A1%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B29-19%E5%86%8D%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=c83d616b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%87%B3%E4%BB%8A%E5%85%B129%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%AB%E4%BF%A1%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B29-19%E5%86%8D%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%2F&h=8406eb61\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/泰國示威至今共29人被捕-被控煽動人權律師不獲保釋-獄中寫信呼籲9-19再集會/</a><br />\n<br />\n全球疫情持續，截至今曰已 101 日沒有本地確診的泰國，數月來則有各種示威「遍地開花」。泰國警方近日多次高調拘捕組織或參與示威的學運人士、人權律師、反政府歌手等等，至今已共拘捕 29 人，其中被控「煽動叛亂」等近 10 項罪名的 35 歲人權律師 Anon Numpha 昨日（3日）於曼谷上庭時，被指因違反保釋條件前往「Free People Movement」的多次示威，而被拒再次保釋，他後來透過代表把一張信條放上社交媒體，指自己在監獄外的責任已完，很高興與泰國人一起抗爭，信亦不忘呼籲眾人 9 月 19 日到泰國國立法政大學再次參與大型集會。"},{"pid":"17ae8365d7da2325686f2cbda6bbc5c9896f6a23","tid":2188891,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/wionews/status/1301789595194077184?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwionews%2Fstatus%2F1301789595194077184%3Fs%3D21&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=aa776d5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwionews%2Fstatus%2F1301789595194077184%3Fs%3D21&h=e7f9ca1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/wionews/status/1301789595194077184?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n改為研究起碼頭同鐵路<br />\n<br />\nA frequently proposed, frequently cancelled plan to build a 100km canal between the Gulf of Thailand and the Andaman Sea is back on the Thai government&rsquo;s radar, after a fashion.<br />\n<br />\nExcept now instead of a waterway the idea is to build two ports linked by a railway.<br />\n<br />\nThe Thai government has approved a budget of $5.3m to study the plan, its transport minister has said.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.globalconstructionreview.com/news/thailand-mulls-replacing-28bn-kra-canal-idea-railw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalconstructionreview.com%2Fnews%2Fthailand-mulls-replacing-28bn-kra-canal-idea-railw%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=387bbceb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.globalconstructionreview.com/news/thailand-mulls-replacing-28bn-kra-canal-idea-railw/</a><br />\n<br />\n連兩隻潛水艇都唔買<br />\n<br />\nKra Canal project, if constructed, would allow China to bypass the Strait of Malacca<br />\n<br />\nPurchase of two Chinese submarines worth USD 724 million delayed<br />\n<br />\nChina losing key allies in Indo-Pacific Region<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.timesnownews.com/international/article/double-blow-for-china-after-thailand-scraps-kra-canal-project-delays-submarine-deal-amid-public-pressure/647466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Finternational%2Farticle%2Fdouble-blow-for-china-after-thailand-scraps-kra-canal-project-delays-submarine-deal-amid-public-pressure%2F647466&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cS